    <abstract>
      <t>This document describes requirements and solutions for MPLS-TP Shared Ring Protection (MSRP) in the ring topology for point-to-point (P2P) services. The mechanism of MSRP is illustrated and analyzed how it satisfies the requirements in RFC6564 [RFC5654] for optimized ring protection.</t>
